<pb n="0777a" ed="T" xml:id="T16.0683.0777a"/>
<lb n="0777a01" ed="T"/>
<milestone n="1" unit="juan"/>
<lb n="0777a02" ed="T"/><cb:docNumber>No. 683</cb:docNumber>
<lb n="0777a03" ed="T"/><cb:juan n="001" fun="open"><cb:mulu n="001" type="卷"/><cb:jhead><title><note n="0777001" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔佛說〕－【三】【宮】＊</note><note n="0777001" resp="CBETA" type="mod">〔佛說〕－【宋】【元】【明】【宮】＊</note><app n="0777001"><lem wit="【大】">佛說</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】"><space quantity="0"/></rdg></app>諸德福田經</title></cb:jhead></cb:juan>
<lb n="0777a04" ed="T"/>
<lb n="0777a05" ed="T"/><byline cb:type="Translator">西晉沙門<note n="0777002" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">（釋）＋法立【三】【宮】</note><note n="0777002" resp="CBETA" type="mod">（釋）＋法立【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0777002"><lem wit="【大】">法立</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】">釋法立</rdg></app>、<note n="0777003" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">法炬共譯＝共法炬譯【元】，法炬同譯【明】</note><note n="0777003" resp="CBETA" type="mod">法炬共譯＝共法炬譯【元】，＝法炬同譯【明】</note><app n="0777003"><lem wit="【大】">法炬共譯</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【元】">共法炬譯</rdg><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【明】">法炬同譯</rdg></app></byline>
<lb n="0777a06" ed="T"/><cb:div type="jing"><p xml:id="pT16p0777a0601">聞如是：</p><p xml:id="pT16p0777a0604" rend="inline">一時佛在舍衛國祇樹給孤獨園，與
<lb n="0777a07" ed="T"/>大<note n="0777004" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">比丘＋（眾）【三】【宮】</note><note n="0777004" resp="CBETA" type="mod">比丘＋（眾）【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0777004"><lem wit="【大】">比丘</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】">比丘眾</rdg></app>千二百五十，菩薩萬人，大眾無數，圍
<lb n="0777a08" ed="T"/>繞說法。爾時天帝釋與諸欲天子三萬二千，
<lb n="0777a09" ed="T"/>各將營從，不可稱數，來詣佛所，稽首于地，
<lb n="0777a10" ed="T"/>皆坐一面。</p><p xml:id="pT16p0777a1005" rend="inline"><note n="0777005" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔爾〕－【三】【宮】</note><note n="0777005" resp="CBETA" type="mod">〔爾〕－【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0777005"><lem wit="【大】">爾</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】"><space quantity="0"/></rdg></app>時天<note n="0777006" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">帝＋（釋）【三】【宮】</note><note n="0777006" resp="CBETA" type="mod">帝＋（釋）【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0777006"><lem wit="【大】">帝</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】">帝釋</rdg></app>察眾坐定，承佛神旨，
<lb n="0777a11" ed="T"/>從<note n="0777007" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">坐而起＝座而興【三】【宮】</note><note n="0777007" resp="CBETA" type="mod">坐而起＝座而興【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0777007"><lem wit="【大】">坐而起</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】">座而興</rdg></app>，整<note n="0777008" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">（衣）＋服【三】【宮】</note><note n="0777008" resp="CBETA" type="mod">（衣）＋服【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0777008"><lem wit="【大】">服</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】">衣服</rdg></app>作禮，長跪叉手，白世尊
<lb n="0777a12" ed="T"/>曰：「欲有所問，唯願彰演垂世軌則！」</p><p xml:id="pT16p0777a1214" rend="inline">佛告天
<lb n="0777a13" ed="T"/>帝：「譬如冥室，不求燈火，焉有所見！善哉問
<lb n="0777a14" ed="T"/>矣，吾當為汝分別說之！」</p><p xml:id="pT16p0777a1410" rend="inline">天帝白佛：「夫人種
<lb n="0777a15" ed="T"/>德，欲求<note n="0777009" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">影＝景【三】【宮】</note><note n="0777009" resp="CBETA" type="mod">影＝景【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0777009"><lem wit="【大】">影</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】">景</rdg></app>福，豈有良田果報無限，種絲髮
<lb n="0777a16" ed="T"/>之德本，獲無量之福乎！唯願天尊敷揚<note n="0777010" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">惠＝慧【三】【宮】</note><note n="0777010" resp="CBETA" type="mod">惠＝慧【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0777010"><lem wit="【大】">惠</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】">慧</rdg></app>
<lb n="0777a17" ed="T"/>訓，令此愚<note n="0777011" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">曚＝矇【宋】【宮】，蒙【元】【明】</note><note n="0777011" resp="CBETA" type="mod">曚＝矇【宋】【宮】，＝蒙【元】【明】</note><app n="0777011"><lem wit="【大】">曚</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【宮】">矇</rdg><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【元】【明】">蒙</rdg></app>福報無量！」</p><p xml:id="pT16p0777a1710" rend="inline">天尊歎曰：「<note n="0777012" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">快＝善【三】【宮】</note><note n="0777012" resp="CBETA" type="mod">快＝善【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0777012"><lem wit="【大】">快</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】">善</rdg></app>哉，
<lb n="0777a18" ed="T"/>天帝！開意所問，法無上矣！諦聽，善思！吾當
<lb n="0777a19" ed="T"/>具演，令汝歡喜。」天帝大眾受教而聽。</p><p xml:id="pT16p0777a1915" rend="inline">佛告
<lb n="0777a20" ed="T"/>天帝：「眾僧<note n="0777013" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔之中〕－【三】【宮】</note><note n="0777013" resp="CBETA" type="mod">〔之中〕－【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0777013"><lem wit="【大】">之中</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】"><space quantity="0"/></rdg></app>，有五淨德，名曰福田。供
<lb n="0777a21" ed="T"/>之得福，進可成佛。何謂為五？一者、發心離
<lb n="0777a22" ed="T"/>俗，懷佩道故；二者、毀其形好，應法服故；三者、
<lb n="0777a23" ed="T"/>永割親愛，無適莫故；四者、委棄軀命，遵<note n="0777014" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">眾善＝崇道【三】【宮】</note><note n="0777014" resp="CBETA" type="mod">眾善＝崇道【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0777014"><lem wit="【大】">眾
<lb n="0777a24" ed="T"/>善</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】">崇道</rdg></app>故；五者、志求大乘，欲度人故。以此五<note n="0777015" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">德＝福【宋】【元】，事【明】【宮】</note><note n="0777015" resp="CBETA" type="mod">德＝福【宋】【元】，＝事【明】【宮】</note><app n="0777015"><lem wit="【大】">德</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】">福</rdg><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【明】【宮】">事</rdg></app>，
<lb n="0777a25" ed="T"/>名曰福田。為良為美，為無<note n="0777016" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">早＝旱【三】【宮】</note><note n="0777016" resp="CBETA" type="mod">早＝旱【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0777016"><lem wit="【大】">早</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】">旱</rdg></app>喪，供之得福，
<lb n="0777a26" ed="T"/>難為喻矣！」</p><p xml:id="pT16p0777a2605" rend="inline">爾時世尊以偈頌曰：</p>
<lb n="0777a27" ed="T"/><lg xml:id="lgT16p0777a2701" rend="margin-left:1em;text-indent:-1em"><l>「毀形守志節，</l><l>割愛無所親，</l>
<lb n="0777a28" ed="T"/><l>出家弘聖道，</l><l>願度一切人，</l>
<lb n="0777a29" ed="T"/><l>五德超世務，</l><l>名曰最福田，</l>
<pb n="0777b" ed="T" xml:id="T16.0683.0777b"/>
<lb n="0777b01" ed="T"/><l>供養獲永安，</l><l>其福第一尊。」</l></lg>
<lb n="0777b02" ed="T"/><p xml:id="pT16p0777b0201">佛告天帝：「復有七法廣施，名曰福田，行者
<lb n="0777b03" ed="T"/>得福，即生梵天。何謂為七？一者、興立佛圖、僧
<lb n="0777b04" ed="T"/>房、堂閣；二者、園果、浴池、樹木清涼；三者、常施
<lb n="0777b05" ed="T"/>醫藥，療救眾病；四者、作<note n="0777017" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">牢堅＝堅牢【三】【宮】</note><note n="0777017" resp="CBETA" type="mod">牢堅＝堅牢【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0777017"><lem wit="【大】">牢堅</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】">堅牢</rdg></app>船，濟度人民；五
<lb n="0777b06" ed="T"/>者、安設橋梁，過度羸弱；六者、近道作井，渴乏
<lb n="0777b07" ed="T"/>得飲；七者、造作圊廁，施便利處。是為七事得
<lb n="0777b08" ed="T"/>梵天福。」</p><p xml:id="pT16p0777b0804" rend="inline">爾時世尊，以偈頌曰：</p>
<lb n="0777b09" ed="T"/><lg xml:id="lgT16p0777b0901" rend="margin-left:1em;text-indent:-1em"><l>「起塔立精舍，</l><l>園果施清涼，</l>
<lb n="0777b10" ed="T"/><l>病則醫藥救，</l><l>橋船度人民，</l>
<lb n="0777b11" ed="T"/><l>曠路作好井，</l><l>渴乏得安身，</l>
<lb n="0777b12" ed="T"/><l>所生食甘露，</l><l>無病常<note n="0777018" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">安寧＝康寧【三】【宮】</note><note n="0777018" resp="CBETA" type="mod">安寧＝康寧【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0777018"><lem wit="【大】">安寧</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】">康寧</rdg></app>，</l>
<lb n="0777b13" ed="T"/><l>造廁施清淨，</l><l>除穢致輕悅，</l>
<lb n="0777b14" ed="T"/><l>後無便利患，</l><l>莫見<note n="0777019" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">穢惡＝惡穢【三】【宮】</note><note n="0777019" resp="CBETA" type="mod">穢惡＝惡穢【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0777019"><lem wit="【大】">穢惡</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】">惡穢</rdg></app>者。</l>
<lb n="0777b15" ed="T"/><l>譬如五河流，</l><l>晝夜無休息，</l>
<lb n="0777b16" ed="T"/><l>此德亦如<note n="0777020" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">斯＝是【三】【宮】</note><note n="0777020" resp="CBETA" type="mod">斯＝是【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0777020"><lem wit="【大】">斯</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】">是</rdg></app>，</l><l>終得昇梵天。」</l></lg>
<lb n="0777b17" ed="T"/><p xml:id="pT16p0777b1701">於時座中有一比丘，名曰聽聰，聞法欣悅，
<lb n="0777b18" ed="T"/>即從坐起，為佛作禮，長跪叉手，白世尊曰：
<lb n="0777b19" ed="T"/>「佛教真諦，洪潤無量。所以者何？我念宿命
<lb n="0777b20" ed="T"/>無數世時，<note n="0777021" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔生〕－【三】【宮】</note><note n="0777021" resp="CBETA" type="mod">〔生〕－【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0777021"><lem wit="【大】">生</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】"><space quantity="0"/></rdg></app>波羅奈國，為長者子。於大道
<lb n="0777b21" ed="T"/>邊，作小精舍，床臥漿<note n="0777022" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">糧＝𤄜【宋】【宮】，糒【元】【明】</note><note n="0777022" resp="CBETA" type="mod">糧＝𤄜【宋】【宮】，＝糒【元】【明】</note><app n="0777022"><lem wit="【大】">糧</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【宮】">𤄜</rdg><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【元】【明】">糒</rdg></app>，供給眾僧，行路
<lb n="0777b22" ed="T"/>頓乏，亦得止息。緣此功德，命終生天，為天帝
<lb n="0777b23" ed="T"/>釋，下生世間，為轉輪聖王，各三十六<note n="0777023" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">反＝返【三】【宮】</note><note n="0777023" resp="CBETA" type="mod">反＝返【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0777023"><lem wit="【大】">反</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】">返</rdg></app>，典
<lb n="0777b24" ed="T"/>領天、人，足下生毛，躡虛而遊，九十一劫，食
<lb n="0777b25" ed="T"/>福自然。今值世尊，顧臨眾生，蠲我愚濁，安
<lb n="0777b26" ed="T"/>以淨慧，生死栽枯，號曰真人，福報誠諦，其
<lb n="0777b27" ed="T"/>為然矣！」</p><p xml:id="pT16p0777b2704" rend="inline">爾時聽聰以偈頌曰：</p>
<lb n="0777b28" ed="T"/><lg xml:id="lgT16p0777b2801" rend="margin-left:1em;text-indent:-1em"><l>「<note n="0777024" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">惟＝唯【宋】【明】</note><app n="0777024"><lem wit="【大】">惟</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【明】">唯</rdg></app>念過去世，</l><l>供養為輕微，</l>
<lb n="0777b29" ed="T"/><l>蒙報歷遐劫，</l><l>餘福值天師。</l>
<pb n="0777c" ed="T" xml:id="T16.0683.0777c"/>
<lb n="0777c01" ed="T"/><l>淨慧斷生死，</l><l>癡愛<note n="0777025" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">情＝消【三】【宮】</note><note n="0777025" resp="CBETA" type="mod">情＝消【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0777025"><lem wit="【大】">情</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】">消</rdg></app>無遺，</l>
<lb n="0777c02" ed="T"/><l>佛恩流無窮，</l><l>是故重自歸。」</l></lg>
<lb n="0777c03" ed="T"/><p xml:id="pT16p0777c0301">於<note n="0777026" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">時＝是【三】【宮】</note><note n="0777026" resp="CBETA" type="mod">時＝是【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0777026"><lem wit="【大】">時</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】">是</rdg></app>聽聰禮已還坐。復有一比丘，名<note n="0777027" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔曰〕－【三】【宮】</note><note n="0777027" resp="CBETA" type="mod">〔曰〕－【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0777027"><lem wit="【大】">曰</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】"><space quantity="0"/></rdg></app>
<lb n="0777c04" ed="T"/>波拘盧，<note n="0777028" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">（即）＋從【三】【宮】</note><note n="0777028" resp="CBETA" type="mod">（即）＋從【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0777028"><lem wit="【大】">從</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】">即從</rdg></app>座而起，整服作禮，長跪叉手，白
<lb n="0777c05" ed="T"/>世尊曰：「我念宿命，生拘夷那竭國，為長者
<lb n="0777c06" ed="T"/>子。時世無佛，眾僧教化，大會說法，我往聽
<lb n="0777c07" ed="T"/>經。聞法歡喜，持一藥果，名<note n="0777029" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">呵梨勒＝阿梨勒【明】</note><app n="0777029"><lem wit="【大】">呵梨勒</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【明】">阿梨勒</rdg></app>，奉上
<lb n="0777c08" ed="T"/>眾僧。緣此果報，命終<note n="0777030" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">昇＝生【三】【宮】</note><note n="0777030" resp="CBETA" type="mod">昇＝生【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0777030"><lem wit="【大】">昇</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】">生</rdg></app>天，下生世間，恒
<lb n="0777c09" ed="T"/>處尊貴，端正雄傑，與眾超絕，九十一劫，未
<lb n="0777c10" ed="T"/>曾<note n="0777031" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">有＝疾【三】【宮】</note><note n="0777031" resp="CBETA" type="mod">有＝疾【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0777031"><lem wit="【大】">有</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】">疾</rdg></app>病。餘福值佛，光導癡冥，授我法藥，逮
<lb n="0777c11" ed="T"/>得應真，力能移山，慧能消惡。善哉福報，為
<lb n="0777c12" ed="T"/>真諦矣！」</p><p xml:id="pT16p0777c1204" rend="inline">爾時波拘盧以偈頌曰：</p>
<lb n="0777c13" ed="T"/><lg xml:id="lgT16p0777c1301" rend="margin-left:1em;text-indent:-1em"><l>「慈澤潤枯槁，</l><l>德勳濟苦<note n="0777032" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">患＝勤【宮】</note><app n="0777032"><lem wit="【大】">患</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宮】">勤</rdg></app>，</l>
<lb n="0777c14" ed="T"/><l>一果之善本，</l><l>享福迄今存。</l>
<lb n="0777c15" ed="T"/><l>佛垂真諦義，</l><l>蒙教超出淵，</l>
<lb n="0777c16" ed="T"/><l>聖眾祐無極，</l><l>稽首上福田。」</l></lg>
<lb n="0777c17" ed="T"/><p xml:id="pT16p0777c1701">於時波拘盧禮已還坐。復有一比丘，名曰
<lb n="0777c18" ed="T"/>須陀耶，即從座起，整服作禮，長跪叉手，白
<lb n="0777c19" ed="T"/>世尊曰：「我自<note n="0777033" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">惟＝唯【明】下同</note><app n="0777033"><lem wit="【大】">惟</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【明】">唯</rdg></app>念先世之時，生維耶離國，
<lb n="0777c20" ed="T"/>為小<note n="0777034" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">家＝民家作【三】【宮】</note><note n="0777034" resp="CBETA" type="mod">家＝民家作【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0777034"><lem wit="【大】">家</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】">民家作</rdg></app>子。時世無佛，眾僧<note n="0777035" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔行〕－【三】【宮】</note><note n="0777035" resp="CBETA" type="mod">〔行〕－【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0777035"><lem wit="【大】">行</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】"><space quantity="0"/></rdg></app>教化。我時
<lb n="0777c21" ed="T"/>持酪，入市欲賣，值遇眾僧，大會講法，過而
<lb n="0777c22" ed="T"/>立聽，法言微妙，聞<note n="0777036" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">之＝則【三】【宮】</note><note n="0777036" resp="CBETA" type="mod">之＝則【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0777036"><lem wit="【大】">之</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】">則</rdg></app>歡悅，即舉瓶酪，布
<lb n="0777c23" ed="T"/>施眾僧。眾僧呪願，益懷欣<note n="0777037" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">踊＝勇【宮】＊</note><app n="0777037"><lem wit="【大】">踊</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宮】">勇</rdg></app>。緣此福<note n="0777038" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">報＝德【宮】</note><app n="0777038"><lem wit="【大】">報</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宮】">德</rdg></app>，
<lb n="0777c24" ed="T"/><note n="0777039" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">壽終生天＝終生天上【三】【宮】</note><note n="0777039" resp="CBETA" type="mod">壽終生天＝終生天上【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0777039"><lem wit="【大】">壽終生天</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】">終生天上</rdg></app>，下<note n="0777040" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">生＝在【三】【宮】</note><note n="0777040" resp="CBETA" type="mod">生＝在【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0777040"><lem wit="【大】">生</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】">在</rdg></app>世間，財富無限，九十一
<lb n="0777c25" ed="T"/>劫，<note n="0777041" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">豪尊榮貴＝豪貴尊榮【三】【宮】</note><note n="0777041" resp="CBETA" type="mod">豪尊榮貴＝豪貴尊榮【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0777041"><lem wit="【大】">豪尊榮貴</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】">豪貴尊榮</rdg></app>。末後餘愆，生於世間，母妊
<lb n="0777c26" ed="T"/>數月，得病命終，埋母塚中，月滿乃生。塚中
<lb n="0777c27" ed="T"/>七年，飲死母乳，用自濟活。微福值佛，開闡
<lb n="0777c28" ed="T"/>明法，超度死地，逮得應真。諦哉罪福，誠如
<lb n="0777c29" ed="T"/>佛教！」</p><p xml:id="pT16p0777c2903" rend="inline">爾時須陀耶以偈頌曰：</p>
<pb n="0778a" ed="T" xml:id="T16.0683.0778a"/>
<lb n="0778a01" ed="T"/><lg xml:id="lgT16p0778a0101" rend="margin-left:1em;text-indent:-1em"><l>「前為小家子，</l><l>賣酪以自存，</l>
<lb n="0778a02" ed="T"/><l>欣<app type="star" corresp="#0777037"><lem wit="【大】">踊</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宮】">勇</rdg></app>施微薄，</l><l>得離三苦患。</l>
<lb n="0778a03" ed="T"/><l>雖罪塚中生，</l><l>飲乳活七年，</l>
<lb n="0778a04" ed="T"/><l>因緣得解脫，</l><l>歸命聖福田。」</l></lg>
<lb n="0778a05" ed="T"/><p xml:id="pT16p0778a0501">於時須陀耶禮已還坐。復有一比丘，名曰
<lb n="0778a06" ed="T"/><note n="0778001" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔阿〕－【宮】</note><app n="0778001"><lem wit="【大】">阿</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宮】"><space quantity="0"/></rdg></app>難，即從座起，整服作禮，長跪叉手，白
<lb n="0778a07" ed="T"/>世尊曰：「我念宿命，生羅閱祇<note n="0778002" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔國〕－【宮】</note><app n="0778002"><lem wit="【大】">國</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宮】"><space quantity="0"/></rdg></app>，為庶民子，
<lb n="0778a08" ed="T"/>身生惡瘡，治之不差。有親友道人，來語我
<lb n="0778a09" ed="T"/>言：『當浴眾僧，取其浴水，以用<note n="0778003" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">洗＝洒【宮】＊</note><app n="0778003"><lem wit="【大】">洗</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宮】">洒</rdg></app>瘡，便可
<lb n="0778a10" ed="T"/><note n="0778004" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">除＝得【三】【宮】</note><note n="0778004" resp="CBETA" type="mod">除＝得【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0778004"><lem wit="【大】">除</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】">得</rdg></app>愈，又可得福！』我即歡喜，往到寺中，加
<lb n="0778a11" ed="T"/>敬至心，更作新井，香油浴具，<note n="0778005" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">洗＝洒【宋】【元】【宮】</note><app n="0778005"><lem wit="【大】">洗</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【宮】">洒</rdg></app>浴眾僧，以
<lb n="0778a12" ed="T"/>汁<app type="star" corresp="#0778003"><lem wit="【大】">洗</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宮】">洒</rdg></app>瘡，尋蒙除愈。從此因緣，所生端正，金
<lb n="0778a13" ed="T"/>色晃昱，不受塵垢，九十一劫，常得淨福，僧
<lb n="0778a14" ed="T"/>祐廣遠。今<note n="0778006" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">復＝得【三】【宮】</note><note n="0778006" resp="CBETA" type="mod">復＝得【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0778006"><lem wit="【大】">復</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】">得</rdg></app>值佛，心垢消滅，逮得應真。」</p><p xml:id="pT16p0778a1416" rend="inline">阿
<lb n="0778a15" ed="T"/>難於佛前以偈頌曰：</p>
<lb n="0778a16" ed="T"/><lg xml:id="lgT16p0778a1601" rend="margin-left:1em;text-indent:-1em"><l>「聖眾為良<note n="0778007" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">醫＝藥【宮】</note><app n="0778007"><lem wit="【大】">醫</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宮】">藥</rdg></app>，</l><l>救濟苦惱患，</l>
<lb n="0778a17" ed="T"/><l><app type="star" corresp="#0778003"><lem wit="【大】">洗</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宮】">洒</rdg></app>浴施清淨，</l><l>瘡愈蒙得安。</l>
<lb n="0778a18" ed="T"/><l>所生常端正，</l><l>殊異紫金顏，</l>
<lb n="0778a19" ed="T"/><l><note n="0778008" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">德＝得【三】【宮】</note><note n="0778008" resp="CBETA" type="mod">德＝得【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0778008"><lem wit="【大】">德</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】">得</rdg></app>潤無<note n="0778009" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">崖＝涯【元】【明】</note><app n="0778009"><lem wit="【大】">崖</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【元】【明】">涯</rdg></app>限，</l><l>歸命良福田。」</l></lg>
<lb n="0778a20" ed="T"/><p xml:id="pT16p0778a2001"><note n="0778010" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">（於時）＋阿難【元】【明】，〔阿〕－【宮】</note><app n="0778010"><lem wit="【大】">阿難</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【元】【明】">於時阿難</rdg><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宮】">難</rdg></app>禮已還坐。爾時座中有一比丘尼，名
<lb n="0778a21" ed="T"/>曰奈女，即從座起，整服作禮，長跪叉手，白
<lb n="0778a22" ed="T"/>佛言：「<note n="0778011" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">我＋（自）【宮】</note><app n="0778011"><lem wit="【大】">我</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宮】">我自</rdg></app>念先世，生波羅奈國，為貧女人。時
<lb n="0778a23" ed="T"/>世有佛，名曰迦葉，時與大眾，圍繞說法。我
<lb n="0778a24" ed="T"/>時在座，聞經歡喜，意欲布施，顧無所有，自
<lb n="0778a25" ed="T"/>惟貧賤，心用悲感，詣他園圃，乞求果<note n="0778012" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">蓏＝菜【三】【宮】</note><note n="0778012" resp="CBETA" type="mod">蓏＝菜【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0778012"><lem wit="【大】">蓏</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】">菜</rdg></app>，當
<lb n="0778a26" ed="T"/>以施佛。時得一奈，大而香好，擎一<note n="0778013" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">盂＝鉢【宋】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0778013"><lem wit="【大】">盂</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【明】【宮】">鉢</rdg></app>水并
<lb n="0778a27" ed="T"/>奈一枚，奉迦葉佛及諸眾僧。佛知至意，呪願
<lb n="0778a28" ed="T"/>受之，分布水、奈，一切周普。緣此福<note n="0778014" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">祚＝德【三】【宮】</note><note n="0778014" resp="CBETA" type="mod">祚＝德【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0778014"><lem wit="【大】">祚</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】">德</rdg></app>，壽盡
<lb n="0778a29" ed="T"/>生天，得為天后。下生世間，不由胞胎，九十
<pb n="0778b" ed="T" xml:id="T16.0683.0778b"/>
<lb n="0778b01" ed="T"/>一劫，生奈華中，端正鮮<note n="0778015" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">淨＝好【三】【宮】</note><note n="0778015" resp="CBETA" type="mod">淨＝好【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0778015"><lem wit="【大】">淨</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】">好</rdg></app>，常識宿命。今值
<lb n="0778b02" ed="T"/>世尊，開示道眼。」</p><p xml:id="pT16p0778b0207" rend="inline">爾時奈女以偈頌曰：</p>
<lb n="0778b03" ed="T"/><lg xml:id="lgT16p0778b0301" rend="margin-left:1em;text-indent:-1em"><l>「三尊慈潤普，</l><l>慧度無男女，</l>
<lb n="0778b04" ed="T"/><l>水果施弘報，</l><l>緣得離眾苦。</l>
<lb n="0778b05" ed="T"/><l>在世生華中，</l><l>上則為天后，</l>
<lb n="0778b06" ed="T"/><l>自歸聖眾祐，</l><l>福田最深厚。」</l></lg>
<lb n="0778b07" ed="T"/><p xml:id="pT16p0778b0701"><note n="0778016" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">（於是）＋比【元】【明】</note><app n="0778016"><lem wit="【大】">比</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【元】【明】">於是比</rdg></app>丘尼奈女禮已還坐。於<note n="0778017" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">時＝是【三】【宮】＊</note><note n="0778017" resp="CBETA" type="mod"><!--CBETA todo type: ＊-->時＝是【宋】【元】【明】【宮】＊</note><app n="0778017"><lem wit="【大】">時</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】">是</rdg></app>天帝即從座
<lb n="0778b08" ed="T"/>起，為佛作禮，白世尊曰：「我先世時，生拘留
<lb n="0778b09" ed="T"/>大國，為長者子。青衣抱行，入城遊觀，值遇
<lb n="0778b10" ed="T"/>眾僧，街巷分衛。時見人民，施者甚多，即自
<lb n="0778b11" ed="T"/>念言：『願得財寶，布施眾僧，不亦快乎！』即解
<lb n="0778b12" ed="T"/><note n="0778018" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">珠瓔＝珠纓【宋】【宮】</note><app n="0778018"><lem wit="【大】">珠瓔</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【宮】">珠纓</rdg></app>，布施眾僧。同心呪願，歡喜而去。從
<lb n="0778b13" ed="T"/>此因緣，壽終即生忉利天上，為天帝釋，九
<lb n="0778b14" ed="T"/>十一劫，永離八難。」</p><p xml:id="pT16p0778b1408" rend="inline">於<app><lem resp="CBETA.maha CBETA.say" wit="【CBETA】【麗】">是<note type="cf1">K12n0366_p0156c17</note><note type="cf2">T16n0683_p0778b24</note></lem><rdg wit="【大】">時</rdg></app><anchor xml:id="fxT16p0778b01"/>天帝以偈頌曰：</p>
<lb n="0778b15" ed="T"/><lg xml:id="lgT16p0778b1501" rend="margin-left:1em;text-indent:-1em"><l>「德高無過者，</l><l>開福塞禍<note n="0778019" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">元＝原【三】【宮】</note><note n="0778019" resp="CBETA" type="mod">元＝原【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0778019"><lem wit="【大】">元</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】">原</rdg></app>，</l>
<lb n="0778b16" ed="T"/><l>聖眾神<note n="0778020" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">定＝足【三】【宮】</note><note n="0778020" resp="CBETA" type="mod">定＝足【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0778020"><lem wit="【大】">定</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】">足</rdg></app>力，</l><l>童幼發歡喜。</l>
<lb n="0778b17" ed="T"/><l>效眾悅意施，</l><l>遷神典二天，</l>
<lb n="0778b18" ed="T"/><l>自歸<note n="0778021" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">世最厚＝聖眾祐【元】【明】</note><app n="0778021"><lem wit="【大】">世最厚</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【元】【明】">聖眾祐</rdg></app>，</l><l>世世願奉尊。」</l></lg>
<lb n="0778b19" ed="T"/><p xml:id="pT16p0778b1901">佛告天帝及諸大眾：「聽我<note n="0778022" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">所＝自【三】【宮】</note><note n="0778022" resp="CBETA" type="mod">所＝自【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0778022"><lem wit="【大】">所</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】">自</rdg></app>說，宿命所行。
<lb n="0778b20" ed="T"/>昔我前世於波羅奈國，<note n="0778023" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">近＝在【三】【宮】</note><note n="0778023" resp="CBETA" type="mod">近＝在【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0778023"><lem wit="【大】">近</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】">在</rdg></app>大道邊，安施圊
<lb n="0778b21" ed="T"/>廁，國中人<note n="0778024" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">民＝眾【宮】</note><app n="0778024"><lem wit="【大】">民</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宮】">眾</rdg></app>，得輕安者，莫不感義。緣此功
<lb n="0778b22" ed="T"/>德，所生<note n="0778025" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">淨＝清【三】【宮】</note><note n="0778025" resp="CBETA" type="mod">淨＝清【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0778025"><lem wit="【大】">淨</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】">清</rdg></app>潔，累劫<note n="0778026" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">行＝修【三】【宮】</note><note n="0778026" resp="CBETA" type="mod">行＝修【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0778026"><lem wit="【大】">行</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】">修</rdg></app>道，穢染不污，功祚
<lb n="0778b23" ed="T"/>大備，自致成佛。金<note n="0778027" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">體光耀＝色光曜【宋】【宮】，色晃晃【元】【明】</note><note n="0778027" resp="CBETA" type="mod">體光耀＝色光曜【宋】【宮】，＝色晃晃【元】【明】</note><app n="0778027"><lem wit="【大】">體光耀</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【宮】">色光曜</rdg><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【元】【明】">色晃晃</rdg></app>，塵水不著，食
<lb n="0778b24" ed="T"/>自消化，無便利之患。」</p><p xml:id="pT16p0778b2409" rend="inline">於是世尊以偈頌曰：</p>
<lb n="0778b25" ed="T"/><lg xml:id="lgT16p0778b2501" rend="margin-left:1em;text-indent:-1em"><l>「忍<note n="0778028" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">穢＝辱【宋】【元】</note><app n="0778028"><lem wit="【大】">穢</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】">辱</rdg></app>修福事，</l><l><app><lem resp="CBETA.maha CBETA.say" wit="【CBETA】【麗】">為<note type="cf1">K12n0366_p0157a05</note><note type="cf2">T12n0387_p1095a08</note></lem><rdg wit="【大】">我</rdg></app>人所不污，</l>
<lb n="0778b26" ed="T"/><l>造廁施便利，</l><l>煩重得輕安。</l>
<lb n="0778b27" ed="T"/><l>此德除貢高，</l><l>因解生死緣，</l>
<lb n="0778b28" ed="T"/><l>進<note n="0778029" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">登＝發【三】【宮】</note><note n="0778029" resp="CBETA" type="mod">登＝發【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0778029"><lem wit="【大】">登</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】">發</rdg></app>成佛道，</l><l>空淨巍巍尊。」</l></lg>
<lb n="0778b29" ed="T"/><p xml:id="pT16p0778b2901">佛告天帝：「九十六種道，佛道最尊；九十六
<pb n="0778c" ed="T" xml:id="T16.0683.0778c"/>
<lb n="0778c01" ed="T"/>種法，<note n="0778030" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">（以）＋佛【三】【宮】</note><note n="0778030" resp="CBETA" type="mod">（以）＋佛【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0778030"><lem wit="【大】">佛</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】">以佛</rdg></app>法最真；九十六種僧，佛僧最正。所
<lb n="0778c02" ed="T"/>以者何？如來從阿僧祇劫，發願誠諦，殞命積
<lb n="0778c03" ed="T"/>德，誓為眾生，國財、妻子、頭目、血肉，以用布
<lb n="0778c04" ed="T"/>施，無戀愛之心。心若虛空，無所不覆，六度、
<lb n="0778c05" ed="T"/>四等眾善普備，德慧成滿，乃得為佛。身色
<lb n="0778c06" ed="T"/>紫金，相好無比；去來現在，無不<note n="0778031" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">照＝昭【宋】【宮】</note><app n="0778031"><lem wit="【大】">照</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【宮】">昭</rdg></app>達；三界
<lb n="0778c07" ed="T"/>尊天，莫能及者；言信德重，震動天地。其有
<lb n="0778c08" ed="T"/>眾生，<note n="0778032" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">發一＝一發【三】【宮】</note><note n="0778032" resp="CBETA" type="mod">發一＝一發【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0778032"><lem wit="【大】">發一</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】">一發</rdg></app>敬心<note n="0778033" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">向＝於【三】【宮】</note><note n="0778033" resp="CBETA" type="mod">向＝於【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0778033"><lem wit="【大】">向</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】">於</rdg></app>如來者，勝獲大千世界
<lb n="0778c09" ed="T"/>之珍寶矣！說三十七品、十二部經，分別罪
<lb n="0778c10" ed="T"/>福，言皆至誠，開三乘教，各得奉行，聞者歡
<lb n="0778c11" ed="T"/>喜，樂作沙門，信佛行法，志尚清高。眾僧之
<lb n="0778c12" ed="T"/>中，有四雙八輩、十二賢者，捨世貪諍，導世
<lb n="0778c13" ed="T"/><note n="0778034" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">開＝間【三】【宮】</note><note n="0778034" resp="CBETA" type="mod">開＝間【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0778034"><lem wit="【大】">開</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】">間</rdg></app>福，天、人路通，眾僧之由矣。是為最尊無
<lb n="0778c14" ed="T"/>上之<note n="0778035" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">道＋（也）【三】【宮】</note><note n="0778035" resp="CBETA" type="mod">道＋（也）【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0778035"><lem wit="【大】">道</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】">道也</rdg></app>，諸佛、菩薩、緣覺、應真皆從中出，教
<lb n="0778c15" ed="T"/>化一切，度脫群生。」</p><p xml:id="pT16p0778c1508" rend="inline">佛說是時，天帝釋眾皆
<lb n="0778c16" ed="T"/>發無上正真道意，不可計人得法眼淨。於是
<lb n="0778c17" ed="T"/>阿難長跪叉手，白<note n="0778036" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">佛＝世尊【三】【宮】</note><note n="0778036" resp="CBETA" type="mod">佛＝世尊【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0778036"><lem wit="【大】">佛</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】">世尊</rdg></app>言：「此名何經？云何奉
<lb n="0778c18" ed="T"/><note n="0778037" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">持＝行【三】【宮】</note><note n="0778037" resp="CBETA" type="mod">持＝行【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0778037"><lem wit="【大】">持</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】">行</rdg></app>？」</p><p xml:id="pT16p0778c1802" rend="inline">佛告阿難：「是經名曰『諸德福田』，<note n="0778038" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">常＝當【三】</note><note n="0778038" resp="CBETA" type="mod">常＝當【宋】【元】【明】</note><app n="0778038"><lem wit="【大】">常</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】">當</rdg></app>奉持
<lb n="0778c19" ed="T"/>之，明宣經道，莫令缺減！」</p><p xml:id="pT16p0778c1910" rend="inline">佛說經已，天帝釋
<lb n="0778c20" ed="T"/>眾、一切眾會，莫不歡喜，作禮而去。</p></cb:div>
<lb n="0778c21" ed="T"/><cb:juan n="001" fun="close"><cb:jhead><title><app type="star" corresp="#0777001"><lem wit="【大】">佛說</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】"><space quantity="0"/></rdg></app>諸德福田經</title></cb:jhead></cb:juan>
</body></text></TEI>